ToDoPet Privacy Policy

Effective Date: March 5, 2025

1. Introduction
ToDoPet Team ("Company") values your privacy and explains in this Privacy Policy ("Policy") the information we collect and how it is used. This Policy is effective as of March 5, 2025.

2. Information We Collect
We collect the following personal information:
- Step Count Data: To provide pet growth features, we collect your step count.
- Photos: We access your photo library to allow you to upload a pet image.
- Advertising ID: We collect an advertising identifier to provide personalized ads.

3. Purpose of Information Use
The collected personal information is used for the following purposes:
- Step Count Data: To provide pet growth features.
- Photos: To upload user pet images.
- Advertising ID: To provide personalized advertisements.

4. Sharing Information with Third Parties
- We share your advertising ID with Google AdMob to provide personalized ads.
- We may share information as required by law in response to legal requests.

5. Data Retention and Security
- Collected personal information is retained for one year after you stop using the Service, after which it is securely deleted.
- We use encryption and other security measures to protect your personal information.

6. Your Rights
- You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal information at any time.
- To request deletion, please send an email to the contact below:
  - Email: todopetcs@gmail.com

7. Changes to the Privacy Policy
- We may update this Policy as necessary, and changes will be announced 7 days before the effective date.
- If you do not agree with the updated Policy, you may discontinue using the Service.

8. Contact Information
For inquiries regarding personal information, please contact us at:
- Email: todopetcs@gmail.com
